{"tid":1088547,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 為重整架構，已解雇了數百名 IT 技術人員。","createTime":"2019-04-02T06:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T12:41:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80aa5c6b262ce5a2fc92763461fe54d3593e3e8c","tid":1088547,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"Intel 前 CEO Brian Krzanich 被爆與下屬有染後離職，CEO 一職懸空了近 7 個月最終在今年 2 月由 Robert Swan 接任，不過這位新 CEO 要面對的問題認真多，首要當然是要解決 10nm 工藝量產停滯不前及 14nm 產能短缺的問題，由於 Intel 公司正積極轉型並調整公司戰略核心，在上週有消息指 Intel 已解雇了數百名 IT 技術人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2019/04/source/0119464909139477152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F04%2Fsource%2F0119464909139477152.jpg&h=67b178f6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n據 Oregonlive 的報導，Intel 官方證實上週裁減了數百名員工，當中包括了 Intel 公司位於俄勒岡州的最大據點，但沒有透露具體的員工數據或受影響的部門，亦沒公佈確實理由，裁員規模可謂 Intel 自 2016 年以來最大的一次。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/17807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F17807&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m61u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=a44326ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/17807</a>"},{"pid":"a7d51779d51552ec1493f120da45f862726cc2ef","tid":1088547,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"Intel 在一份簡短的聲明中承認在俄勒岡州的裁減部份員工，並表示&ldquo;我們的員工隊伍的變化是由我們不斷評估的業務需求和優先事項所驅動的，我們致力於以專業和尊重的態度對待所有受影響的員工。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱 Intel 是次裁員並非為了節省成本，主要是與內部技術系統管理模式改變有關，消息提到 Intel 已決定把所有營運整合與印度技術巨頭 Infosys 的單一承包商，這意味著在承包商數量將會減少，因此無需再聘用太多的管理人員進行監督。<br />\n <br />\n不過，Intel 在今年 1 月公佈的 2019 財年收入指引略遜於預期，引發了市場對 Intel 公司營收上的擔憂， Intel CEO Robert Swan 在未上任前亦曾表示公司需要調整核心架構保持競爭力，在未來將會由以 PC 為中心轉型成為以數據為中心的公司，改變為客戶服務的方式，以及尋求合作研發最好的技術。"},{"pid":"85e39cf84959c21c7785dc9de886220d3cce38c3","tid":1088547,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"幾時到hsbc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf100fe255e0a98f06d4f785066e2d66b1af9cf","tid":1088547,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"另一方面intel 請左好多勁人<br />\n<br />\ne.g. athlon k7 ryzen 設計師，hardocp 個reviewer"},{"pid":"499efd091f7809701b0397e6b700a864fe7d0e0a","tid":1088547,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85e39cf84959c21c7785dc9de886220d3cce38c3","tid":1088547,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"幾時到hsbc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"年年都到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94e96695c71d51caa8d7508e51a4cd295b291e6","tid":1088547,"uid":54378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165521f9d14b66eca9df45be69c9bc0b010ca2cf","tid":1088547,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"牙膏唧曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}